---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="About | IGA — Revenue Engineering Partner" description="Revenue engineering partner born from a St. Maarten mindset. Three founders combining marketing, strategy, and business development to build revenue systems.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="pt-32 pb-16 lg:pt-40 lg:pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="fade-up max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-iga-blue mb-4">About IGA</p>
        <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-medium tracking-tight mb-8">
          Born from a mindset shaped in St. Maarten
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          The island's motto is <em class="text-iga-blue not-italic font-medium">Semper pro Grediens</em> — always progressing. This is not just a phrase to us. It defines how we operate.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="gradient-line"></div>

  <!-- Origin Story -->
  <section class="py-24 lg:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24">
        <div class="fade-up space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Coming from an environment where nothing is handed to you, we learned early that if you want to compete globally, you prepare differently, you work harder, and you stay disciplined. Progress is not optional — it is necessary.
          </p>
          <p>
            Sports — especially football — played a big role in shaping how we think and operate. You don't win by being loud. You win by preparing, studying the opponent, building strategy, training consistently, and executing with precision.
          </p>
          <p>
            When something doesn't work, you adjust, you refine, and you continue. This mentality is the foundation of IGA.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-up fade-up-delay-2">
          <div class="border-l-2 border-iga-blue pl-8 py-4">
            <p class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl text-gray-800 italic leading-snug mb-4">
              "We saw that most agencies move fast but lack depth. They focus on surface metrics and chase activity instead of outcomes."
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 font-medium">— The IGA Founders</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why we exist -->
  <section class="py-24 lg:py-32 bg-iga-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="fade-up max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight mb-8">We built IGA to change that</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          We don't run random campaigns. We build revenue systems.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Before launching anything, we study the business like it's our own. We analyze the product, positioning, buyers, competitors, and identify where revenue is leaking across acquisition, qualification, conversion, and retention.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-6 mt-16">
        <div class="fade-up bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">We build</p>
          <p class="font-serif text-lg font-medium text-white mt-1">Systems, not campaigns</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fade-up fade-up-delay-1 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">We focus on</p>
          <p class="font-serif text-lg font-medium text-white mt-1">Revenue, not vanity</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fade-up fade-up-delay-2 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">We start with</p>
          <p class="font-serif text-lg font-medium text-white mt-1">Understanding, not assumptions</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fade-up fade-up-delay-3 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">We cover</p>
          <p class="font-serif text-lg font-medium text-white mt-1">The full journey</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fade-up fade-up-delay-4 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">We are</p>
          <p class="font-serif text-lg font-medium text-white mt-1">Partners, not vendors</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission -->
  <section class="py-24 lg:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center fade-up">
      <p class="text-sm font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-iga-blue mb-6">Our Mission</p>
      <p class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-snug tracking-tight">
        To help businesses grow through engineered marketing systems that deliver <em class="text-iga-blue not-italic">measurable</em> and <em class="text-iga-blue not-italic">predictable</em> revenue.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Founders -->
  <section class="py-24 lg:py-32 bg-iga-grey/20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="fade-up max-w-2xl mb-16">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-iga-blue mb-4">The Team</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight mb-6">Built by three founders</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Each founder contributes to building systems, understanding businesses deeply, and delivering measurable outcomes. Not a service provider — a growth partner.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="fade-up card-hover group">
          <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-iga-grey/50 mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="text-center text-gray-400">
              <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-2 opacity-30" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0zM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0114.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0112 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632z"/></svg>
              <p class="text-sm">Photo</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-medium">Founder</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-iga-blue font-medium mt-1">Marketing & Growth</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fade-up fade-up-delay-1 card-hover group">
          <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-iga-grey/50 mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="text-center text-gray-400">
              <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-2 opacity-30" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0zM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0114.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0112 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632z"/></svg>
              <p class="text-sm">Photo</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-medium">Founder</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-iga-blue font-medium mt-1">Strategy & Systems</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fade-up fade-up-delay-2 card-hover group">
          <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-iga-grey/50 mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="text-center text-gray-400">
              <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-2 opacity-30" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0zM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0114.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0112 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632z"/></svg>
              <p class="text-sm">Photo</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-medium">Founder</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-iga-blue font-medium mt-1">Business Development</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-24 lg:py-32 bg-iga-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center fade-up">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight mb-6">Ready to work with us?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-10">Let's talk about your business and where the growth opportunities are.</p>
      <a href={`${base}contact`} class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-iga-blue text-iga-black px-8 py-4 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-iga-blue-light transition-colors">
        Schedule a Strategy Session
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 17L17 7M17 7H7M17 7v10"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
